<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>9 SPEED AND 10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON 16709 AND 16710 SERIES - INSTALL - SHIFTER HOUSING</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="4">
        <title>SHIFTER HOUSING</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place all three mainshaft sliding clutches in the neutral position (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13021l1">Figure 211</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13021l1" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13021l1" filename="../figg13/G13021L1.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 211. Sliding Clutches In Neutral Position</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install shifter housing gasket in position on the case. With all three shift yokes in the
                neutral position, install the shifter housing assembly on the case, fitting the shift yokes into the
                slots of the corresponding sliding clutches (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13021l2">Figure 212</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13021l2" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13021l2" filename="../figg13/G13021L2.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 212. Shifter Housing Assembly</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Apply Loctite 242 or equivalent to the bolt threads. Install the bolts in shifter housing
                and tighten to 35 to 45 ft-lbs. (47 to 61 N&#8226; m) (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13021l3">Figure213</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13021l3" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13021l3" filename="../figg13/G13021L3.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 213. Bolts In Shifter Housing</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the shift tower gasket and the three detent balls and springs (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13021l4">Figure 214</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13021l4" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13021l4" filename="../figg13/G13021L4.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 214. Detent Balls &#38; Springs</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
